[semihtml][title]Your Activism Cause Here[/title]
The Lovinity Community+ aims to be a community that promotes activist causes and movements. Everyone who uses our website is free to promote positive activist movements. However, if you would like an activist section on our website, you may contact us via. support tickets (About -&gt; Support Tickets, or email support@lovinity.org ). By getting an activist section / page on our website, your cause will gain extra exposure as well as the use of our website features. Here are some of the possible features we can delegate to your activist section / page:

<ul>
	<li>Club user group (so people can show their support via. their profile)</li>
	<li>Advertising banners (for a fee)</li>
	<li>Events Calendar</li>
	<li>Catalogues / forms / databases</li>
	<li>Chat rooms</li>
	<li>Forums</li>
	<li>Downloads</li>
	<li>Audio / Video / Image galleries</li>
	<li>Links library</li>
	<li>News</li>
	<li>Web Pages (Comcode pages)</li>
	<li>Polls</li>
	<li>Wikis</li>
	<li>Internet Radio Show</li>
</ul>

